# Common Interview Questions 🔥

### Why implement Stack using Linked List?

Answer:

```text
Dynamic size
O(1) insertion/deletion
```

---

### Why maintain Rear pointer in Queue?

Answer:

```text
To make enqueue O(1)
```

---

### Difference between Stack and Queue?

| Stack               | Queue                    |
| ------------------- | ------------------------ |
| LIFO                | FIFO                     |
| Same end operations | Different end operations |

