# 🧠 Today's Core Understanding

### Doubly Linked List

* prev + next pointers
* move both directions

### Stack using Linked List

* head acts as top
* push/pop = O(1)

### Queue using Linked List

* front + rear pointers
* enqueue/dequeue = O(1)

